1
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:15,780
♪Trap my frame♪

2
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:20,060
♪Plagues demand I bow in shame♪

3
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:22,940
♪Snare my soul♪

4
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:27,100
♪Rules command I swallow my pride♪

5
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:30,620
♪Mock my way♪

6
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:34,060
♪Chained me where I must stay♪

7
00:00:34,420 --> 00:00:36,780
♪Taught me to kneel, not to speak♪

8
00:00:37,020 --> 00:00:41,220
♪And to let my life pass by in silence♪

9
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:44,100
♪But I heard the wind♪

10
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:45,900
♪From the sea and the sky♪

11
00:00:46,180 --> 00:00:47,660
♪It said don't bend♪

12
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:49,820
♪Bow your head, and your chains begin♪

13
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:51,380
♪You are the wave♪

14
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,300
♪And the wind that won't behave♪

15
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:56,340
♪How could you be chained?♪

16
00:00:56,740 --> 00:00:58,740
♪Untamed, uncaged, unclaimed♪

17
00:00:58,780 --> 00:01:00,540
♪You're the blade in my gaze♪

18
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:02,420
♪This world will leave you no space♪

19
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,220
♪Then pierce it with your blaze♪

20
00:01:04,220 --> 00:01:06,100
♪My silent grind♪

21
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:08,060
♪My aching pain♪

22
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:10,300
♪Will one day turn...♪

23
00:01:11,860 --> 00:01:14,620
♪I am who I am♪

24
00:01:14,620 --> 00:01:18,140
♪My greatest ambition♪

25
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:21,300
♪If the world can't contain me♪

26
00:01:21,380 --> 00:01:24,940
♪Then I'll break through it♪

27
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:27,100
♪Become who I am♪

28
00:01:27,100 --> 00:01:27,860
[Wild Ambition Bloom]

29
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from Stone and Water's novel,
The Uncaged Flame]

30
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 1]

31
00:01:34,580 --> 00:01:38,380
[1916, Qizhou]

32
00:01:42,140 --> 00:01:44,660
Three jin of Muxiang
for one jin of Xiangfu? What a drop.

33
00:01:44,660 --> 00:01:45,340
Shaohua,

34
00:01:45,540 --> 00:01:46,540
there's an opera going on over there.

35
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:47,900
Let's check it out.

36
00:01:52,180 --> 00:01:53,060
Mr. Xia is here.

37
00:01:55,020 --> 00:01:55,900
Who is he?

38
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:56,820
Mr. Xia.

39
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:57,900
Do you know him?

40
00:01:58,100 --> 00:01:59,420
Anyone from Qizhou in this trade

41
00:01:59,420 --> 00:02:01,580
knows Mr. Xia Yuan
at Shouyuan Apothecary.

42
00:02:02,700 --> 00:02:03,780
If one day,

43
00:02:04,420 --> 00:02:06,380
I could be as influential as him,

44
00:02:07,460 --> 00:02:08,820
that would be great.

45
00:02:10,100 --> 00:02:10,980
Good day, Mr. Xia.

46
00:02:25,140 --> 00:02:25,780
Erniu.

47
00:02:30,420 --> 00:02:31,140
Erniu.

48
00:02:32,260 --> 00:02:33,060
The horse's going wild!

49
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:34,540
Watch out! Get out of the way!

50
00:02:34,540 --> 00:02:35,540
Move! The horse is startled!

51
00:02:36,380 --> 00:02:37,100
Run!

52
00:02:37,780 --> 00:02:38,500
Look out!

53
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:02,260
Watch out!

54
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:09,660
Niu!

55
00:03:10,460 --> 00:03:11,020
Niu.

56
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:12,620
Are you okay?

57
00:03:13,820 --> 00:03:14,540
You alright?

58
00:03:15,820 --> 00:03:17,820
Thanks. Go on, thank her too.

59
00:03:17,940 --> 00:03:18,620
It's nothing.

60
00:03:19,180 --> 00:03:19,860
Thank you.

61
00:03:20,900 --> 00:03:21,380
Let's go.

62
00:03:27,340 --> 00:03:28,180
Let me help you.

63
00:03:28,180 --> 00:03:28,740
Thanks.

64
00:03:41,260 --> 00:03:41,860
Thanks.

65
00:03:44,100 --> 00:03:44,660
Really, thank you.

66
00:04:02,100 --> 00:04:03,660
Then I'll pay a deposit first.

67
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:06,020
[Tang's Apothecary]
Please send this to Tongfu Goods Depot.

68
00:04:06,380 --> 00:04:07,500
No can do, buddy.

69
00:04:07,820 --> 00:04:09,540
Guandong Trade Guild has a rule.

70
00:04:09,540 --> 00:04:12,300
We require full payment before delivery.

71
00:04:12,900 --> 00:04:13,660
Don't worry.

72
00:04:13,780 --> 00:04:15,340
We are the Guandong Trade Guild.

73
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:17,660
What you see is what you'll get.

74
00:04:18,780 --> 00:04:19,340
Alright.

75
00:04:19,420 --> 00:04:21,220
Please step inside to settle up.

76
00:04:23,980 --> 00:04:25,620
Sir, if I were you,

77
00:04:25,620 --> 00:04:27,220
I'd shop around a bit before paying.

78
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:29,060
Miss, thank you.

79
00:04:29,260 --> 00:04:30,500
I've checked several places.

80
00:04:30,500 --> 00:04:32,100
Mr. Tang's goods are quite genuine

81
00:04:32,100 --> 00:04:32,900
and the price is fair.

82
00:04:33,220 --> 00:04:33,740
But...

83
00:04:33,820 --> 00:04:34,420
It's okay.

84
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:36,980
Does it have anything to do with you?

85
00:04:37,220 --> 00:04:38,220
Why are you meddling?

86
00:04:39,260 --> 00:04:40,460
Ugh, just my luck.

87
00:04:40,460 --> 00:04:41,300
What a jinx.

88
00:04:41,300 --> 00:04:42,100
Who are you swearing at?

89
00:04:42,860 --> 00:04:43,900
You,

90
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:45,620
a bad luck magnet.

91
00:04:45,780 --> 00:04:46,740
How dare you mess with my business!

92
00:04:46,740 --> 00:04:47,180
Alright.

93
00:04:47,180 --> 00:04:48,860
Selling fake Huangqi
and you've got the nerve to argue?

94
00:04:48,860 --> 00:04:49,780
Nonsense!

95
00:04:50,780 --> 00:04:53,140
Look, the surface lines

96
00:04:53,140 --> 00:04:55,420
are dyed yellow.

97
00:04:55,540 --> 00:04:58,060
The cross-section
may look like a gold-in-silver pattern,

98
00:04:58,100 --> 00:04:59,420
but there's no pith inside.

99
00:04:59,460 --> 00:05:00,820
And these rays,

100
00:05:00,980 --> 00:05:03,180
look, have no cracks.

101
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:07,660
You're from the Qizhou Trade Guild,
aren't you?

102
00:05:09,580 --> 00:05:10,500
Listen up, everyone.

103
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:12,540
Guandong Trade Guild never sells fakes!

104
00:05:12,540 --> 00:05:13,140
That's right.

105
00:05:13,260 --> 00:05:15,140
The Qizhou Trade Guild
can't match us in business,

106
00:05:15,580 --> 00:05:17,540
so now they're slandering us!

107
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:19,500
I swear I'll make you pay for this.

108
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:20,140
I...

109
00:05:20,300 --> 00:05:21,540
Please stop, Mr. Tang.

110
00:05:21,540 --> 00:05:23,260
What you're selling isn't Huangqi.

111
00:05:23,460 --> 00:05:24,980
It's alfalfa roots that he's selling!

112
00:05:24,980 --> 00:05:26,740
That's absolutely impossible.

113
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:27,700
I'll...

114
00:05:27,980 --> 00:05:28,860
Let me show you.

115
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,020
What the heck is going on?

116
00:05:33,020 --> 00:05:33,580
I...

117
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:38,180
Someone's framing me.

118
00:05:38,460 --> 00:05:40,020
It's a setup, buddy.

119
00:05:44,260 --> 00:05:44,900
Ma'am,

120
00:05:45,260 --> 00:05:46,780
may I ask if you've seen

121
00:05:46,780 --> 00:05:48,420
a lady about my height

122
00:05:48,420 --> 00:05:49,980
wearing coarse cloth clothes?

123
00:05:50,340 --> 00:05:51,180
No,

124
00:05:51,420 --> 00:05:52,060
I don't remember.

125
00:05:52,060 --> 00:05:52,780
Shaohua.

126
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:54,380
Erniu.

127
00:05:54,980 --> 00:05:55,940
Where have you been?

128
00:05:55,940 --> 00:05:57,340
I've been looking for you for ages.

129
00:05:57,340 --> 00:05:58,740
Same here.

130
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:00,500
What happened to your face?

131
00:06:02,220 --> 00:06:02,860
It's nothing.

132
00:06:04,500 --> 00:06:05,100
Here.

133
00:06:05,260 --> 00:06:06,140
Have it before it gets cold.

134
00:06:06,140 --> 00:06:07,140
I saved it just for you.

135
00:06:07,140 --> 00:06:08,420
A fried flatbread.

136
00:06:08,860 --> 00:06:09,660
Where'd you get the money

137
00:06:09,660 --> 00:06:10,860
for such expensive food?

138
00:06:11,620 --> 00:06:13,940
Stop asking. Just dig in.

139
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,420
Is everything okay?

140
00:06:18,300 --> 00:06:18,900
Yeah.

141
00:06:19,380 --> 00:06:20,620
It's definitely not!

142
00:06:21,380 --> 00:06:22,780
I'll tell you in a couple of days.

143
00:06:22,780 --> 00:06:23,460
Fine.

144
00:06:23,460 --> 00:06:24,660
I'll wait a few days too.

145
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:26,060
You've got news too?

146
00:06:26,660 --> 00:06:28,940
[Chichun Apothecary]

147
00:06:31,900 --> 00:06:32,500
Shaozhong,

148
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:35,540
why did you buy so much Huangqi?

149
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:36,380
It was cheap.

150
00:06:37,260 --> 00:06:38,860
What exactly happened?

151
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:40,940
The seller was rushing home,

152
00:06:40,940 --> 00:06:42,100
so he let me have it all for cheap.

153
00:06:42,540 --> 00:06:43,580
Perfect for making Miracle Pills.

154
00:06:44,140 --> 00:06:45,580
You've paid for it?

155
00:06:46,740 --> 00:06:47,940
The goods have been delivered.

156
00:06:47,940 --> 00:06:49,020
How could I not pay?

157
00:06:49,780 --> 00:06:51,300
There aren't any traps, right?

158
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:52,780
You didn't buy fake stuff, did you?

159
00:06:53,580 --> 00:06:56,180
I checked everything myself.

160
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:57,020
It's all real.

161
00:06:57,540 --> 00:06:59,140
If you don't believe me, take a look.

162
00:07:05,660 --> 00:07:06,220
How is it?

163
00:07:07,140 --> 00:07:07,820
I'm right, aren't I?

164
00:07:09,660 --> 00:07:10,420
But

165
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:13,700
one picul is enough for the pills.

166
00:07:13,700 --> 00:07:14,940
Why did you buy so much?

167
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:16,940
The seller said

168
00:07:17,060 --> 00:07:18,620
if I took all the goods

169
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:19,860
he had,

170
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:21,700
he'd sell them to me
for 50 silver dollars per picul.

171
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:23,220
I thought about it

172
00:07:23,420 --> 00:07:25,460
and figured, why not just take it all?

173
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:29,860
Four hundred silver dollars?

174
00:07:30,180 --> 00:07:31,540
Where did you get so much money?

175
00:07:31,540 --> 00:07:32,500
From our accounts,

176
00:07:32,700 --> 00:07:34,420
plus I found a way to raise some more.

177
00:07:34,780 --> 00:07:35,340
It was just enough.

178
00:07:35,980 --> 00:07:36,500
Then

179
00:07:37,020 --> 00:07:38,940
you found a broker
from Anke Hall, right?

180
00:07:39,500 --> 00:07:40,660
Are you silly?

181
00:07:41,260 --> 00:07:42,540
The seller and I

182
00:07:42,540 --> 00:07:43,740
are already dealing directly.

183
00:07:43,940 --> 00:07:46,020
Why should I give Anke Hall

184
00:07:46,020 --> 00:07:47,180
a two percent commission?

185
00:07:47,500 --> 00:07:48,340
Besides,

186
00:07:48,780 --> 00:07:50,580
even if I were willing
to waste that money,

187
00:07:50,660 --> 00:07:51,940
the seller might not go for it.

188
00:07:51,940 --> 00:07:54,380
What if something goes wrong?

189
00:07:54,380 --> 00:07:55,660
The Huangqi is all here.

190
00:07:55,820 --> 00:07:56,820
What could possibly go wrong?

191
00:07:59,100 --> 00:08:01,220
[Guandong Guild Hall]

192
00:08:01,220 --> 00:08:02,500
Are you still not telling the truth?

193
00:08:02,780 --> 00:08:05,140
I don't know. Really.

194
00:08:05,220 --> 00:08:07,580
This is clearly your doing.

195
00:08:07,700 --> 00:08:08,700
If I ever faked something,

196
00:08:08,700 --> 00:08:09,540
I, Tang Yaoji,

197
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:11,300
would let a carriage run me over
the moment I stepped outside!

198
00:08:11,300 --> 00:08:12,980
Mr. Yang, Tang is framed.

199
00:08:13,420 --> 00:08:14,100
Our Huangqi

200
00:08:14,100 --> 00:08:16,060
is packed outside the pass
and then shipped to Qizhou.

201
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:17,820
The sacks all have our secret mark.

202
00:08:18,340 --> 00:08:18,900
Look.

203
00:08:19,820 --> 00:08:21,700
The mark on this sack
is crude and sloppy.

204
00:08:21,900 --> 00:08:22,980
It's a forgery for sure.

205
00:08:26,540 --> 00:08:27,820
Indeed!

206
00:08:30,500 --> 00:08:33,300
Someone must have swapped our Huangqi.

207
00:08:33,540 --> 00:08:34,340
Qizhou Trade Guild.

208
00:08:35,220 --> 00:08:36,900
How dare they.

209
00:08:37,820 --> 00:08:40,780
Tang Yaoji, you're just a coward.

210
00:08:40,780 --> 00:08:42,180
You sell fake goods,

211
00:08:42,460 --> 00:08:45,020
and now no one wants

212
00:08:45,140 --> 00:08:46,220
to do business with you.

213
00:08:46,220 --> 00:08:47,660
How's that our problem?

214
00:08:47,660 --> 00:08:49,700
Knock it out, Yi Dajin.

215
00:08:50,260 --> 00:08:51,740
You think I don't know

216
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:53,500
about the dirty tricks you pulled?

217
00:08:53,500 --> 00:08:54,180
Come on, let's fight!

218
00:08:54,180 --> 00:08:55,260
Get them!

219
00:09:11,180 --> 00:09:11,900
Take them down!

220
00:09:12,380 --> 00:09:13,460
Hit them hard!

221
00:09:21,420 --> 00:09:23,380
Who's making such a scene here?

222
00:09:23,380 --> 00:09:25,620
- Mr. Yang.
- Mr. Yang.

223
00:09:26,660 --> 00:09:27,340
Mr. Yang.

224
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:33,780
Mr. Xia.

225
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:38,980
Since you're here,

226
00:09:40,100 --> 00:09:41,940
I'll settle

227
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:45,860
all the old scores with you.

228
00:09:46,860 --> 00:09:49,900
It seems there's a misunderstanding.

229
00:09:51,340 --> 00:09:52,780
Wasn't it you?

230
00:09:53,220 --> 00:09:55,180
You swapped Tang's Huangqi

231
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:57,700
and ruined the reputation
of Guandong Trade Guild.

232
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:58,820
I

233
00:09:59,620 --> 00:10:01,300
have nothing to do with that.

234
00:10:07,500 --> 00:10:08,580
Who took him away?

235
00:10:08,580 --> 00:10:09,980
It seems like the Qizhou Trade Guild.

236
00:10:09,980 --> 00:10:10,820
Why?

237
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:13,780
They say Shaozhong swapped
the Guandong Trade Guild's

238
00:10:13,980 --> 00:10:15,620
real Huangqi with fake stuff.

239
00:10:16,660 --> 00:10:17,820
How is that possible?

240
00:10:17,940 --> 00:10:19,700
Shaozhong was taken away.

241
00:10:19,700 --> 00:10:21,020
What should we do?

242
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:24,820
Mr. Yang, you are convinced

243
00:10:25,260 --> 00:10:28,140
that we were behind it.

244
00:10:28,420 --> 00:10:29,180
So,

245
00:10:29,700 --> 00:10:31,180
I sent people to spread the word

246
00:10:31,340 --> 00:10:32,940
that I would buy Huangqi
at a high price.

247
00:10:34,220 --> 00:10:34,820
Look.

248
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:36,380
This Chu guy took the bait.

249
00:10:36,580 --> 00:10:37,780
He was caught red-handed

250
00:10:38,140 --> 00:10:39,420
when the goods were delivered today.

251
00:10:39,460 --> 00:10:40,220
Mr. Xia.

252
00:10:40,700 --> 00:10:43,140
I spent real money on that Huangqi.

253
00:10:44,140 --> 00:10:44,780
Right.

254
00:10:45,260 --> 00:10:46,180
He refuses to admit it.

255
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:47,340
I believe

256
00:10:47,340 --> 00:10:48,620
much is still unanswered.

257
00:10:49,700 --> 00:10:52,140
But regardless, the Guandong Trade Guild

258
00:10:52,140 --> 00:10:54,380
and your reputation have been restored.

259
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:58,380
Today, these are returned intact.

260
00:10:59,020 --> 00:11:00,980
You can deal with him as you wish.

261
00:11:01,500 --> 00:11:03,420
Wang, have you seen my brother?

262
00:11:03,940 --> 00:11:05,900
He is tied up on Yaowang Temple Street!

263
00:11:06,300 --> 00:11:07,340
Go check on him.

264
00:11:10,060 --> 00:11:11,020
Shameless.

265
00:11:11,620 --> 00:11:12,980
No conscience whatsoever.

266
00:11:12,980 --> 00:11:13,500
Exactly!

267
00:11:13,500 --> 00:11:14,220
Serves him right!

268
00:11:14,540 --> 00:11:15,180
You fraud.

269
00:11:15,180 --> 00:11:16,700
- You're rotten to the core.
- You're beneath contempt.

270
00:11:21,620 --> 00:11:22,500
Make way.

271
00:11:23,340 --> 00:11:24,100
Stop!

272
00:11:24,420 --> 00:11:25,380
Stop throwing!

273
00:11:25,540 --> 00:11:26,420
Cut it out!

274
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:27,660
Enough!

275
00:11:27,820 --> 00:11:28,300
Shaohua.

276
00:11:28,300 --> 00:11:28,860
Shaozhong.

277
00:11:28,860 --> 00:11:29,700
Save me.

278
00:11:29,740 --> 00:11:31,020
What's happening now?

279
00:11:31,300 --> 00:11:32,700
Mr. Yang
from the Guandong Trade Guild said

280
00:11:32,820 --> 00:11:33,740
he'll tie me up here

281
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:34,580
for three days as a public display

282
00:11:34,580 --> 00:11:35,980
and then lynch me.

283
00:11:36,060 --> 00:11:36,820
What?

284
00:11:37,420 --> 00:11:38,900
Quick, help me prove I'm innocent.

285
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:41,100
I swear I didn't swap their Huangqi!

286
00:11:41,580 --> 00:11:43,300
If I'd known it was stolen stuff,

287
00:11:43,460 --> 00:11:44,740
I wouldn't have touched it.

288
00:11:44,900 --> 00:11:46,900
Shaozhong, I'll get you out of this.

289
00:11:47,620 --> 00:11:48,820
[Guandong Guild Hall]

290
00:11:49,740 --> 00:11:51,420
Mr. Yang doesn't want to see you.
Please leave.

291
00:11:51,420 --> 00:11:53,540
Just need to speak up for my brother.

292
00:11:53,540 --> 00:11:54,620
What else is there to say?

293
00:11:55,020 --> 00:11:57,060
He faked the medicine. So outrageous.

294
00:11:57,060 --> 00:11:57,860
It's a capital offense.

295
00:11:57,860 --> 00:11:59,940
Wait, Huangqi is common everywhere.

296
00:12:00,140 --> 00:12:01,780
What makes you think that Huangqi

297
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:02,860
is from the Guandong Trade Guild?

298
00:12:02,860 --> 00:12:04,700
Does your Huangqi

299
00:12:04,700 --> 00:12:05,740
have anything carved on it?

300
00:12:06,580 --> 00:12:08,100
There's no carving on the Huangqi,

301
00:12:08,620 --> 00:12:09,540
but on the sack

302
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:11,100
is our secret mark.

303
00:12:11,860 --> 00:12:12,460
Get out of the way.

304
00:12:15,060 --> 00:12:16,740
Who exactly sold you that Huangqi?

305
00:12:16,740 --> 00:12:17,980
It was a Mr. Huang

306
00:12:17,980 --> 00:12:19,300
from the northwest.

307
00:12:19,420 --> 00:12:19,940
He

308
00:12:20,300 --> 00:12:21,380
stayed

309
00:12:21,380 --> 00:12:22,180
at Yunlai Inn.

310
00:12:22,340 --> 00:12:23,700
[Yunlai Inn]
Mr. Huang from the northwest?

311
00:12:24,300 --> 00:12:25,340
He left a long time ago.

312
00:12:25,540 --> 00:12:26,700
When did he leave?

313
00:12:26,740 --> 00:12:28,100
Several days ago.

314
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:32,140
Then who delivered
those eight piculs of Huangqi?

315
00:12:32,220 --> 00:12:33,820
[Tongda Carriage Depot]
He hired a carter.

316
00:12:33,860 --> 00:12:35,140
Which carter? What did he look like?

317
00:12:35,180 --> 00:12:36,580
He had a mole
at the corner of his mouth.

318
00:12:36,980 --> 00:12:38,620
And on his chest was a character "Da".

319
00:12:40,500 --> 00:12:41,260
Chichun Apothecary?

320
00:12:41,380 --> 00:12:43,460
Yes, a total
of eight piculs of Huangqi.

321
00:12:43,700 --> 00:12:45,100
That's right.

322
00:12:45,420 --> 00:12:46,460
Who hired you?

323
00:12:47,140 --> 00:12:48,940
It was a Mr. Huang.

324
00:12:49,220 --> 00:12:49,860
Where is he now?

325
00:12:49,980 --> 00:12:51,060
I wouldn't know that.

326
00:12:51,060 --> 00:12:52,500
Dropped off the goods, got paid,

327
00:12:52,500 --> 00:12:53,900
never saw him again.

328
00:12:54,100 --> 00:12:55,340
Where was the Huangqi

329
00:12:55,340 --> 00:12:57,020
shipped from?

330
00:12:57,020 --> 00:12:58,140
That was far away.

331
00:12:58,540 --> 00:12:59,300
Fifty li south

332
00:12:59,300 --> 00:13:00,300
of here,

333
00:13:00,300 --> 00:13:01,260
there's Maliu Village.

334
00:13:01,540 --> 00:13:02,860
At the east end of the village,

335
00:13:02,940 --> 00:13:03,500
there's a household.

336
00:13:40,900 --> 00:13:41,620
Mr. Tang, good morning.

337
00:13:41,780 --> 00:13:42,620
Did Mr. Yang get up?

338
00:13:42,620 --> 00:13:43,220
He's been up for a while.

339
00:13:43,220 --> 00:13:43,980
Okay. Hey.

340
00:13:43,980 --> 00:13:44,580
Mr. Yang.

341
00:13:44,580 --> 00:13:45,060
You can't go in.

342
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:45,860
Mr. Yang.

343
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:47,500
The one who switched the Huangqi

344
00:13:47,500 --> 00:13:48,700
definitely wasn't Chu Shaozhong.

345
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:50,620
Who do you think you are

346
00:13:51,980 --> 00:13:53,820
to act all bold in front of me?

347
00:13:53,980 --> 00:13:54,740
Get her out!

348
00:13:55,540 --> 00:13:56,260
Go.

349
00:13:56,540 --> 00:13:57,020
Leave.

350
00:13:57,020 --> 00:13:59,300
Everyone says

351
00:13:59,300 --> 00:14:00,580
you have great judgment.

352
00:14:00,660 --> 00:14:02,220
Didn't expect
you'd fall for someone's trick.

353
00:14:02,460 --> 00:14:03,220
Wait.

354
00:14:06,540 --> 00:14:07,460
Who are you?

355
00:14:09,220 --> 00:14:11,620
I am Chu Shaozhong's younger sister,
Chu Shaohua.

356
00:14:12,260 --> 00:14:13,060
I know you.

357
00:14:14,060 --> 00:14:16,180
Mr. Yang, she's the one

358
00:14:16,180 --> 00:14:17,300
who claimed I sold fake Huangqi.

359
00:14:17,500 --> 00:14:18,460
She even hit my guy.

360
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:19,900
Thank you, Mr. Tang, for recognizing me.

361
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:20,660
Sure, whatever.

362
00:14:21,060 --> 00:14:24,140
If my brother did swap the Huangqi,

363
00:14:24,260 --> 00:14:25,620
then shouldn't I be

364
00:14:25,820 --> 00:14:28,140
counting my money quietly by now?

365
00:14:28,140 --> 00:14:30,260
I exposed Mr. Tang's Huangqi as fake.

366
00:14:30,260 --> 00:14:31,940
Didn't that make you all alert?

367
00:14:33,180 --> 00:14:35,980
Perhaps you didn't know he was involved.

368
00:14:35,980 --> 00:14:37,540
If you'd slipped,

369
00:14:37,660 --> 00:14:39,540
you'd have wrecked his luck.

370
00:14:39,540 --> 00:14:40,260
That makes sense.

371
00:14:40,380 --> 00:14:41,380
But I found the place

372
00:14:41,380 --> 00:14:42,900
where the fake Huangqi was made.

373
00:14:43,180 --> 00:14:44,580
How did you find it?

374
00:14:45,580 --> 00:14:47,180
Although the merchant

375
00:14:47,180 --> 00:14:48,180
who sold Shaozhong fake Huangqi

376
00:14:48,180 --> 00:14:49,540
is now nowhere to be found,

377
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:52,300
I found Maliu Village 50 li away
through Zhu,

378
00:14:52,540 --> 00:14:54,460
a carter from Tongda Carriage Depot.

379
00:14:54,540 --> 00:14:55,580
There's a courtyard.

380
00:14:56,220 --> 00:14:58,100
The tenant's gone,

381
00:14:58,340 --> 00:14:59,540
but the courtyard

382
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:01,180
still has alfalfa roots, dyes,

383
00:15:01,180 --> 00:15:02,180
and tools,

384
00:15:02,340 --> 00:15:03,660
clear proof

385
00:15:03,660 --> 00:15:06,140
it was used to make fake Huangqi.

386
00:15:15,060 --> 00:15:16,460
Your brother faked the goods.

387
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:18,420
Of course you knew where he did it.

388
00:15:18,540 --> 00:15:20,860
No need to ask a carter
to track it down.

389
00:15:20,860 --> 00:15:22,820
I spoke to the landlord myself.

390
00:15:22,860 --> 00:15:25,540
He said the tenant
was from the northwest.

391
00:15:25,540 --> 00:15:26,940
It wasn't Chu Shaozhong.

392
00:15:28,380 --> 00:15:30,580
What if he hired a north-westerner

393
00:15:30,580 --> 00:15:32,260
to rent it for him?

394
00:15:32,540 --> 00:15:33,100
Fine.

395
00:15:34,260 --> 00:15:36,860
Then, how do you explain this?

396
00:15:37,380 --> 00:15:38,540
What do you mean by this?

397
00:15:39,220 --> 00:15:40,980
I found this in the courtyard.

398
00:15:40,980 --> 00:15:42,660
A sack used for holding fake Huangqi.

399
00:15:43,100 --> 00:15:44,660
Everyone says your sacks

400
00:15:44,660 --> 00:15:45,700
have a secret mark.

401
00:15:45,940 --> 00:15:47,660
It also has one.

402
00:15:47,780 --> 00:15:48,620
At first glance,

403
00:15:48,700 --> 00:15:50,420
it's exactly like your secret mark.

404
00:15:50,540 --> 00:15:52,580
But the details give it away.

405
00:15:59,180 --> 00:15:59,940
Mr. Yang, look.

406
00:16:00,780 --> 00:16:02,580
This sloppy mark

407
00:16:03,020 --> 00:16:03,940
seems to come from the same hand

408
00:16:04,020 --> 00:16:05,460
that forged Tang's.

409
00:16:07,100 --> 00:16:08,740
What's so strange about that?

410
00:16:09,100 --> 00:16:11,340
He was swapping the goods.

411
00:16:11,420 --> 00:16:14,220
Naturally, he'd forge the mark.

412
00:16:14,220 --> 00:16:16,180
To fake the mark,

413
00:16:16,260 --> 00:16:17,500
he had to know

414
00:16:17,500 --> 00:16:19,740
the Guandong Guild stamped their sacks.

415
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:21,380
Then why didn't he replace the sacks

416
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:22,940
when he sold the real Huangqi?

417
00:16:23,180 --> 00:16:24,140
Well...

418
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:25,500
Who would have known?

419
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:28,020
Mr. Yang,

420
00:16:28,820 --> 00:16:30,460
Shaozhong did buy stolen goods,

421
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:32,020
but it was an unintentional mistake.

422
00:16:32,220 --> 00:16:33,380
However, if you insist

423
00:16:33,580 --> 00:16:35,340
he is the one who swapped them,

424
00:16:35,340 --> 00:16:36,860
then you're letting
the real culprit walk free.

425
00:16:43,780 --> 00:16:45,980
It's all because of the Huang guy.

426
00:16:47,020 --> 00:16:48,220
If I see him again,

427
00:16:49,140 --> 00:16:50,140
I won't let him off the hook.

428
00:16:52,180 --> 00:16:54,340
I just hate that my money's gone

429
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:56,740
for nothing.

430
00:16:58,740 --> 00:17:00,300
Let's just consider it a lesson learned.

431
00:17:01,220 --> 00:17:02,140
From now on,

432
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:04,100
if something seems too good to be true,

433
00:17:04,820 --> 00:17:06,420
we need to be more careful.

434
00:17:07,900 --> 00:17:09,340
Thankfully, we have Chichun Apothecary.

435
00:17:10,180 --> 00:17:11,460
Let's start small

436
00:17:11,740 --> 00:17:13,940
and make up for the losses first.

437
00:17:14,500 --> 00:17:16,980
Things will keep picking up
for our business.

438
00:17:20,260 --> 00:17:21,020
Shaohua.

439
00:17:21,620 --> 00:17:23,460
There's one more thing
I need to tell you.

440
00:17:23,460 --> 00:17:24,220
Shaozhong!

441
00:17:24,300 --> 00:17:25,140
What are you doing?

442
00:17:25,140 --> 00:17:26,420
Shaozhong!

443
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:27,220
- What are you doing?
- Shaozhong!

444
00:17:27,580 --> 00:17:28,220
- Shaozhong!
- Shaohua!

445
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:29,340
Shaohua!

446
00:17:29,340 --> 00:17:30,140
- Don't you move.
- Shaozhong!

447
00:17:30,300 --> 00:17:30,860
Let me go!

448
00:17:30,860 --> 00:17:32,060
What do you think you are doing?

449
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,460
Get your hands off me!

450
00:17:33,660 --> 00:17:34,340
Let go of me!

451
00:17:34,340 --> 00:17:34,940
Get inside!

452
00:17:35,460 --> 00:17:36,220
Stop it!

453
00:17:37,140 --> 00:17:37,900
Shaohua!

454
00:17:38,060 --> 00:17:38,660
Shaozhong!

455
00:17:43,460 --> 00:17:44,140
Shaozhong!

456
00:17:45,500 --> 00:17:46,140
Shaozhong!

457
00:17:49,380 --> 00:17:50,460
Didn't you say

458
00:17:51,140 --> 00:17:53,420
they agreed to release him?

459
00:17:54,020 --> 00:17:56,180
He got snatched by loan sharks.

460
00:17:56,700 --> 00:17:59,900
How did it come to that?

461
00:18:02,620 --> 00:18:05,060
Shaozhong spent 400 silver dollars

462
00:18:05,460 --> 00:18:06,580
on the Huangqi.

463
00:18:07,900 --> 00:18:09,340
Three hundred and sixty dollars
of the money

464
00:18:09,780 --> 00:18:11,100
came from a loan.

465
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:13,300
Repayment was due in half a month,

466
00:18:13,500 --> 00:18:14,340
with a five li rate.

467
00:18:14,780 --> 00:18:16,140
It's

468
00:18:17,860 --> 00:18:19,180
three days overdue.

469
00:18:20,060 --> 00:18:21,340
By their rules,

470
00:18:21,340 --> 00:18:23,860
three days late, they take a hand.

471
00:18:26,660 --> 00:18:28,100
But don't worry.

472
00:18:28,180 --> 00:18:29,540
I talked to them.

473
00:18:29,540 --> 00:18:31,180
They agreed to give us three more days.

474
00:18:31,460 --> 00:18:32,940
After that,

475
00:18:33,140 --> 00:18:34,300
we have to pay everything:

476
00:18:34,300 --> 00:18:35,220
principal, interest, and a penalty.

477
00:18:35,220 --> 00:18:36,620
A total

478
00:18:36,620 --> 00:18:38,060
of 390 silver dollars.

479
00:18:38,420 --> 00:18:39,100
If we don't,

480
00:18:39,220 --> 00:18:40,420
Shaozhong loses

481
00:18:40,420 --> 00:18:41,700
a hand and a foot.

482
00:18:43,140 --> 00:18:46,660
Then how can he make it?

483
00:18:46,660 --> 00:18:48,700
Three hundred and ninety silver dollars.

484
00:18:49,620 --> 00:18:51,140
The most valuable things we've got

485
00:18:51,140 --> 00:18:53,020
are the land and this house.

486
00:18:53,460 --> 00:18:54,860
I've already been to the broker house

487
00:18:54,860 --> 00:18:57,980
and asked around,
relatives, neighbors, everyone.

488
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:58,780
All in all,

489
00:18:58,780 --> 00:19:00,620
we should be able to pull together
a bit over 100.

490
00:19:01,580 --> 00:19:04,020
If he can't survive this,

491
00:19:04,020 --> 00:19:07,260
I don't want to either.

492
00:19:08,300 --> 00:19:09,100
Mother,

493
00:19:09,340 --> 00:19:11,700
take out
whatever you've managed to save.

494
00:19:11,700 --> 00:19:14,060
I don't have any money

495
00:19:14,060 --> 00:19:16,580
But you still have some jewelry, right?

496
00:19:18,780 --> 00:19:20,540
Those aren't worth much.

497
00:19:20,540 --> 00:19:21,260
Look.

498
00:19:21,260 --> 00:19:21,940
Isn't that...?

499
00:19:22,060 --> 00:19:23,420
Don't push her.

500
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:24,460
If she had any money,

501
00:19:24,460 --> 00:19:26,060
she would've spent it on the family.

502
00:19:26,220 --> 00:19:26,740
Then

503
00:19:26,900 --> 00:19:29,420
what about you?
Don't you have any private savings?

504
00:19:36,260 --> 00:19:37,260
What do you mean?

505
00:19:37,420 --> 00:19:38,980
Let me see what else can be sold.

506
00:19:44,100 --> 00:19:45,420
Then let's sell Chichun Apothecary.

507
00:19:46,980 --> 00:19:47,740
What?

508
00:19:48,340 --> 00:19:49,540
I heard Shaozhong say

509
00:19:49,900 --> 00:19:51,540
that someone was willing to offer 200

510
00:19:51,540 --> 00:19:52,980
to buy Chichun Apothecary.

511
00:19:54,340 --> 00:19:55,500
We can't sell it.

512
00:19:55,980 --> 00:19:57,740
If we don't, he's as good as dead.

513
00:19:59,820 --> 00:20:03,060
That's our family's legacy
for three generations!

514
00:20:03,740 --> 00:20:05,460
No one's selling it!

515
00:20:07,460 --> 00:20:08,460
But if he's gone,

516
00:20:08,500 --> 00:20:09,860
what's the point of keeping it?

517
00:20:10,780 --> 00:20:13,060
Let's sell it.

518
00:20:14,100 --> 00:20:17,380
As long as Shaozhong comes back safe,

519
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:20,140
forget Chichun Apothecary,

520
00:20:20,140 --> 00:20:21,860
sell me if you have to.

521
00:20:21,860 --> 00:20:24,260
I'll sell it!

522
00:20:24,300 --> 00:20:25,140
Take it all!

523
00:20:25,260 --> 00:20:26,220
I'll do it tomorrow.

524
00:20:29,020 --> 00:20:31,060
This is our family's treasure,

525
00:20:31,060 --> 00:20:33,180
the recipe for the Miracle Pill.

526
00:20:33,780 --> 00:20:34,580
I want to learn it.

527
00:20:34,580 --> 00:20:38,140
But I need to tell you this.

528
00:20:38,620 --> 00:20:42,860
A man of honor always keeps striving,
like heaven never stops moving.

529
00:20:42,980 --> 00:20:43,820
Grandpa,

530
00:20:43,820 --> 00:20:47,060
I am a woman, not a man.

531
00:20:47,540 --> 00:20:51,300
To serve the greater good
and live with compassion,

532
00:20:51,700 --> 00:20:53,060
when the heart shines bright,

533
00:20:53,580 --> 00:20:56,100
honor belongs to all.

534
00:20:57,300 --> 00:20:59,300
Grandpa, I want
to be someone honorable too,

535
00:20:59,300 --> 00:21:00,500
to do something that truly matters.

536
00:21:00,780 --> 00:21:02,700
[Chichun Apothecary]
Chichun Apothecary.

537
00:21:02,940 --> 00:21:05,460
Chichun Apothecary.

538
00:21:11,740 --> 00:21:12,460
Mr. Wang.

539
00:21:13,220 --> 00:21:13,860
Thank you.

540
00:21:14,780 --> 00:21:16,860
I'll pay it back soon.

541
00:21:17,100 --> 00:21:17,940
Don't mention it.

542
00:21:18,580 --> 00:21:20,340
I wish

543
00:21:20,620 --> 00:21:21,780
I could do more.

544
00:21:22,500 --> 00:21:23,380
I'm truly sorry.

545
00:21:23,380 --> 00:21:24,540
Please don't say that.

546
00:21:24,940 --> 00:21:25,980
Your help means a lot.

547
00:21:26,540 --> 00:21:28,140
We're truly grateful.

548
00:21:28,300 --> 00:21:29,380
Mrs. Chu,

549
00:21:30,780 --> 00:21:32,300
are you home?

550
00:21:34,060 --> 00:21:35,020
Mrs. San.

551
00:21:35,500 --> 00:21:36,060
I'm here

552
00:21:36,060 --> 00:21:37,660
to bring you a message.

553
00:21:38,220 --> 00:21:39,980
My grandson went
to the Medicine Market this morning.

554
00:21:40,140 --> 00:21:40,980
Guess what?

555
00:21:41,300 --> 00:21:43,100
He met Master Chen.

556
00:21:43,260 --> 00:21:44,980
He asked my grandson
to deliver a message

557
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:47,140
that he'll bring his eldest son

558
00:21:47,140 --> 00:21:48,380
to visit tomorrow.

559
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:49,580
The Chen family?

560
00:21:50,500 --> 00:21:50,980
Is it

561
00:21:51,540 --> 00:21:53,580
the Chen family that Shaohua is arranged
to be married into?

562
00:21:54,220 --> 00:21:55,500
Who else could it be?

563
00:21:55,580 --> 00:21:56,980
Get prepared.

564
00:21:57,020 --> 00:21:58,420
Make sure they don't show up tomorrow

565
00:21:58,460 --> 00:21:59,220
and find you with nothing ready.

566
00:21:59,260 --> 00:22:00,260
I'm going home. Got cooking to do.

567
00:22:00,700 --> 00:22:01,460
Understood.

568
00:22:01,740 --> 00:22:02,980
Goodbye, Mrs. San.

569
00:22:04,540 --> 00:22:08,140
She said Master Chen is coming.

570
00:22:08,140 --> 00:22:08,660
Well...

571
00:22:09,300 --> 00:22:09,820
Mother.

572
00:22:10,460 --> 00:22:11,460
There's hope for Shaozhong.

573
00:22:11,940 --> 00:22:12,940
What do you mean?

574
00:22:12,980 --> 00:22:15,220
Think about it.
They're coming to propose.

575
00:22:15,700 --> 00:22:17,180
They'll have to bring
betrothal gifts, right?.

576
00:22:17,220 --> 00:22:18,220
That means Shaozhong's going to be okay.

577
00:22:21,780 --> 00:22:23,100
If that's the case,

578
00:22:23,100 --> 00:22:24,460
that would be wonderful.

579
00:22:24,620 --> 00:22:25,580
Definitely.

580
00:22:27,340 --> 00:22:28,100
But

581
00:22:28,740 --> 00:22:30,020
we haven't been in touch

582
00:22:30,060 --> 00:22:32,260
with the Chen family for years.

583
00:22:32,860 --> 00:22:34,740
Shaohua mentioned earlier

584
00:22:35,380 --> 00:22:38,020
they might have something else in mind.

585
00:22:38,060 --> 00:22:38,780
That won't do.

586
00:22:40,100 --> 00:22:41,420
No matter what,

587
00:22:41,540 --> 00:22:43,180
this marriage must be finalized.

588
00:22:47,620 --> 00:22:49,860
- Look how perfect it is.
- It's stunning.

589
00:22:50,340 --> 00:22:51,180
Come on. Be good.

590
00:22:51,220 --> 00:22:52,380
Sit here.

591
00:22:52,380 --> 00:22:53,220
Sit down.

592
00:22:54,940 --> 00:22:55,700
Come on.

593
00:22:55,860 --> 00:22:57,500
Master Chen gave this bracelet

594
00:22:57,540 --> 00:22:59,020
when the engagement was made years ago.

595
00:22:59,060 --> 00:22:59,740
I don't want it.

596
00:22:59,780 --> 00:23:00,220
- No.
- Put it on.

597
00:23:00,260 --> 00:23:01,060
Be a good girl, alright?

598
00:23:01,060 --> 00:23:01,740
Just put it on, okay?

599
00:23:02,220 --> 00:23:03,340
So fitting.

600
00:23:03,340 --> 00:23:04,020
Wear it.

601
00:23:04,060 --> 00:23:04,580
Mother.

602
00:23:04,780 --> 00:23:06,300
Go greet Mr. Chen at the door.

603
00:23:06,780 --> 00:23:07,380
Right.

604
00:23:09,300 --> 00:23:11,220
Let's put on some lipstick.

605
00:23:13,100 --> 00:23:15,020
My goodness, what are you doing?

606
00:23:15,220 --> 00:23:16,340
Don't go against me.

607
00:23:17,340 --> 00:23:18,140
Be a good girl.

608
00:23:18,540 --> 00:23:19,260
Come on.

609
00:23:20,060 --> 00:23:20,980
Don't move.

610
00:23:22,060 --> 00:23:22,860
Mrs. Chu.

611
00:23:23,380 --> 00:23:25,380
We haven't seen each other
in over ten years, have we?

612
00:23:25,380 --> 00:23:26,220
Indeed.

613
00:23:26,300 --> 00:23:28,900
I didn't expect you to come so soon.

614
00:23:29,340 --> 00:23:30,620
Since it's a special occasion,

615
00:23:30,620 --> 00:23:32,060
we couldn't wait to come early.

616
00:23:32,500 --> 00:23:33,060
Alright.

617
00:23:33,460 --> 00:23:35,180
Dashun, this is Mrs. Chu.

618
00:23:35,220 --> 00:23:35,740
Mrs. Chu.

619
00:23:36,220 --> 00:23:36,900
Good to see you.

620
00:23:37,540 --> 00:23:38,180
Please come in.

621
00:23:38,220 --> 00:23:38,620
Alright.

622
00:23:38,620 --> 00:23:39,100
Please.

623
00:23:39,540 --> 00:23:39,980
Let's go.

624
00:23:40,020 --> 00:23:40,700
Come in, please.

625
00:23:40,820 --> 00:23:41,780
Shaohua.

626
00:23:43,060 --> 00:23:43,540
Oh my goodness.

627
00:23:43,980 --> 00:23:45,220
How could they have come so soon?

628
00:23:46,140 --> 00:23:47,380
What are you doing?

629
00:23:47,380 --> 00:23:48,140
They're here.

630
00:23:48,140 --> 00:23:50,300
You can't let him see you
looking like that.

631
00:23:51,540 --> 00:23:52,820
Let me tell you, Chu Shaohua,

632
00:23:52,980 --> 00:23:54,700
you must win Chen Dashun's heart.

633
00:23:54,780 --> 00:23:56,700
Think about Shaozhong's hand and foot.

634
00:23:56,820 --> 00:23:57,540
Did you hear me?

635
00:23:57,820 --> 00:23:59,740
Zhou Yan, come here. Hurry.

636
00:24:03,220 --> 00:24:03,820
Go.

637
00:24:04,100 --> 00:24:04,940
Coming.

638
00:24:06,060 --> 00:24:07,180
Hurry up.

639
00:24:09,820 --> 00:24:11,820
I suppose you're Mr. Chen, right?

640
00:24:12,020 --> 00:24:12,460
This is...?

641
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:13,380
My daughter-in-law.

642
00:24:14,060 --> 00:24:14,780
Sir,

643
00:24:15,260 --> 00:24:16,220
if I were you,

644
00:24:16,260 --> 00:24:18,180
I'd shop around a bit before paying.

645
00:24:19,540 --> 00:24:21,180
Shaozhong's wife. Glad to meet you.

646
00:24:21,220 --> 00:24:21,820
Zhou Yan.

647
00:24:25,500 --> 00:24:26,460
This must be Dashun, right?

648
00:24:28,300 --> 00:24:29,300
Oh my.

649
00:24:29,700 --> 00:24:31,260
So dashing.

650
00:24:32,780 --> 00:24:33,300
Shaohua.

651
00:24:33,500 --> 00:24:34,900
Meet Dashun and Mr. Chen.

652
00:24:35,820 --> 00:24:36,500
Mr. Chen.

653
00:24:37,220 --> 00:24:37,820
Da...

654
00:24:38,780 --> 00:24:39,540
Dashun.

655
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:41,220
This is...

656
00:24:41,260 --> 00:24:42,300
- Shaohua.
- Miss Chu.

657
00:24:42,300 --> 00:24:43,220
- Yes.
- Shaohua.

658
00:24:44,220 --> 00:24:45,780
In the blink of an eye, she's grown up.

659
00:24:51,100 --> 00:24:51,900
Allow me.

660
00:24:52,060 --> 00:24:52,900
Here, I'll take them.

661
00:24:53,540 --> 00:24:54,700
Please come inside, Mr. Chen.

662
00:24:54,820 --> 00:24:55,220
Dashun.

663
00:24:55,220 --> 00:24:55,580
Alright.

664
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:56,900
Please.

665
00:24:57,100 --> 00:24:58,020
Mr. Chen, please.

666
00:24:58,460 --> 00:24:59,060
- Please.
- Alright.

667
00:25:01,220 --> 00:25:01,820
Mother.

668
00:25:04,540 --> 00:25:05,220
Hurry.

669
00:25:05,980 --> 00:25:06,940
Shaohua, come in.

670
00:25:09,460 --> 00:25:10,500
Please take a seat, Mr. Chen,

671
00:25:10,500 --> 00:25:11,580
Dashun.

672
00:25:11,580 --> 00:25:12,700
Please.

673
00:25:13,740 --> 00:25:14,500
Mrs. Chu,

674
00:25:14,500 --> 00:25:16,940
I should've visited you long ago.

675
00:25:17,180 --> 00:25:20,180
But business has kept us so busy.

676
00:25:20,180 --> 00:25:21,300
Dashun and I

677
00:25:21,540 --> 00:25:23,020
just couldn't get away.

678
00:25:23,220 --> 00:25:24,620
Year after year,

679
00:25:25,180 --> 00:25:26,660
it's been delayed until today.

680
00:25:27,140 --> 00:25:28,660
It's alright, Mr. Chen.

681
00:25:28,980 --> 00:25:30,620
Good things don't happen in a hurry.

682
00:25:31,380 --> 00:25:33,780
Mrs. Chu, we're here today

683
00:25:33,820 --> 00:25:38,580
because of Dashun and Miss Chu.

684
00:25:39,220 --> 00:25:40,340
That's right, Mr. Chen.

685
00:25:40,660 --> 00:25:42,660
Look, they're not

686
00:25:42,660 --> 00:25:43,420
getting any younger.

687
00:25:43,980 --> 00:25:45,380
Time to get things underway.

688
00:25:47,380 --> 00:25:48,380
Well,

689
00:25:49,420 --> 00:25:51,700
you see,

690
00:25:51,940 --> 00:25:55,140
back then, it was just a casual remark

691
00:25:55,140 --> 00:25:57,980
between your father-in-law and me.

692
00:25:58,220 --> 00:25:59,020
A joke, really.

693
00:26:01,140 --> 00:26:02,220
That's right, Mr. Chen.

694
00:26:02,420 --> 00:26:03,860
But you know,

695
00:26:04,020 --> 00:26:06,100
you're well respected

696
00:26:06,380 --> 00:26:08,420
around here.

697
00:26:08,540 --> 00:26:09,780
And my grandpa-in-law,

698
00:26:10,340 --> 00:26:12,020
although I never met him,

699
00:26:12,060 --> 00:26:14,460
was also a well-known figure.

700
00:26:14,620 --> 00:26:16,260
So, whatever

701
00:26:16,260 --> 00:26:17,540
you said,

702
00:26:17,820 --> 00:26:19,940
even if it was a joke,

703
00:26:20,060 --> 00:26:21,820
still carries real weight.

704
00:26:23,140 --> 00:26:25,860
Times have changed,

705
00:26:26,500 --> 00:26:28,820
and young people these days

706
00:26:28,820 --> 00:26:30,620
care more about love than tradition.

707
00:26:31,380 --> 00:26:32,900
What matchmakers say

708
00:26:32,900 --> 00:26:33,860
and what parents decide

709
00:26:34,420 --> 00:26:36,820
don't always hold weight anymore.

710
00:26:37,500 --> 00:26:38,740
Mr. Chen, let me tell you,

711
00:26:38,940 --> 00:26:41,900
Dashun must be satisfied with Shaohua.

712
00:26:42,220 --> 00:26:42,940
Isn't that right?

713
00:26:44,420 --> 00:26:45,380
Are you satisfied, Dashun?

714
00:26:48,540 --> 00:26:49,940
Mother, see?

715
00:26:50,860 --> 00:26:52,020
They're

716
00:26:52,100 --> 00:26:53,580
a destined match.

717
00:26:53,580 --> 00:26:55,860
He is satisfied with Shaohua.

718
00:26:55,860 --> 00:26:56,580
That's right.

719
00:26:59,340 --> 00:27:00,340
Mr. Chen, come on.

720
00:27:00,340 --> 00:27:01,500
Have some tea.

721
00:27:01,900 --> 00:27:03,260
To be honest with you, Mr. Chen,

722
00:27:03,500 --> 00:27:04,580
many people

723
00:27:04,620 --> 00:27:06,140
came here

724
00:27:06,140 --> 00:27:07,340
just to gossip.

725
00:27:07,540 --> 00:27:09,460
They say that back then,

726
00:27:09,460 --> 00:27:11,380
you came to propose willingly

727
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:13,100
drawn

728
00:27:13,100 --> 00:27:14,540
by our former prestige.

729
00:27:14,540 --> 00:27:15,780
But now, our family

730
00:27:15,780 --> 00:27:17,060
isn't what it used to be,

731
00:27:17,140 --> 00:27:18,380
while you've grown

732
00:27:18,380 --> 00:27:20,180
more prosperous by the day.

733
00:27:20,260 --> 00:27:23,060
So they say you'll go back on your word.

734
00:27:23,220 --> 00:27:24,900
I was really upset with them

735
00:27:25,060 --> 00:27:26,700
and told them not to talk nonsense.

736
00:27:27,020 --> 00:27:28,740
Mr. Chen is not that kind of person.

737
00:27:29,060 --> 00:27:29,900
Right, Mr. Chen?

738
00:27:30,020 --> 00:27:30,820
Enjoy the tea.

739
00:27:31,060 --> 00:27:32,380
Dashun, have some tea.

740
00:27:35,980 --> 00:27:36,700
Mr. Chen,

741
00:27:37,580 --> 00:27:39,980
how about we settle things today?

742
00:27:41,060 --> 00:27:43,180
Mother, I checked the lunar calendar.

743
00:27:43,780 --> 00:27:46,900
The 18th of the fifth month and the 20th
of the sixth month are perfect.

744
00:27:47,620 --> 00:27:48,140
Mother.

745
00:27:52,220 --> 00:27:53,420
This is serious.

746
00:27:53,420 --> 00:27:56,300
Let's give this
some more thought, Mrs. Chu.

747
00:27:56,700 --> 00:28:00,260
Mr. Chen, you've met Shaohua,

748
00:28:00,460 --> 00:28:02,580
and Dashun couldn't be more willing.

749
00:28:02,700 --> 00:28:05,140
What else is left to discuss,

750
00:28:05,220 --> 00:28:06,020
right?

751
00:28:07,700 --> 00:28:09,780
It's getting late.

752
00:28:12,540 --> 00:28:14,180
Dashun and I

753
00:28:14,540 --> 00:28:16,500
still have some business
to take care of.

754
00:28:16,700 --> 00:28:18,700
Let's wrap it up here

755
00:28:18,700 --> 00:28:19,500
for today.

756
00:28:19,500 --> 00:28:20,140
Wait.

757
00:28:20,180 --> 00:28:22,860
Mr. Chen, the key issue's still hanging.

758
00:28:23,380 --> 00:28:24,460
We'll talk about it next time.

759
00:28:24,940 --> 00:28:25,580
Mrs. Chu,

760
00:28:25,580 --> 00:28:26,300
well,

761
00:28:26,780 --> 00:28:28,220
I'll take my leave.

762
00:28:28,220 --> 00:28:28,980
- Dashun.
- Father.

763
00:28:28,980 --> 00:28:29,700
Let's go.

764
00:28:29,940 --> 00:28:30,780
- Wait.
- Come on.

765
00:28:31,180 --> 00:28:32,700
Mr. Chen.

766
00:28:33,340 --> 00:28:34,340
Mrs. Chu, we're leaving.

767
00:28:34,340 --> 00:28:34,700
Alright.

768
00:28:36,020 --> 00:28:36,620
But...

769
00:28:36,620 --> 00:28:38,180
Wait, Mr. Chen.

770
00:28:38,660 --> 00:28:39,860
Mother.

771
00:28:40,020 --> 00:28:40,500
Mr. Chen.

772
00:28:40,500 --> 00:28:41,140
Mrs. Chu Junior,

773
00:28:41,260 --> 00:28:42,780
in your condition,
there's no need to see us off.

774
00:28:42,780 --> 00:28:44,020
Mr. Chen.

775
00:28:44,220 --> 00:28:45,140
Please hear me out.

776
00:28:45,540 --> 00:28:47,060
Please, don't trouble yourself.

777
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:47,660
Mr. Chen.

778
00:28:48,500 --> 00:28:49,500
Please hear me out.

779
00:28:49,620 --> 00:28:50,540
I mean...

780
00:28:50,540 --> 00:28:51,380
- Mr. Chen.
- No need.

781
00:28:51,580 --> 00:28:53,700
You get what I mean.

782
00:28:53,780 --> 00:28:55,500
And I get yours.

783
00:28:55,500 --> 00:28:56,700
Let's

784
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:57,740
talk over the marriage

785
00:28:57,740 --> 00:28:59,140
another time, alright?

786
00:28:59,140 --> 00:29:00,500
We can't afford to delay!

787
00:29:01,420 --> 00:29:02,980
No, Mr. Chen, I mean,

788
00:29:02,980 --> 00:29:04,500
with Dashun here,

789
00:29:04,620 --> 00:29:06,380
let's make their marriage official.

790
00:29:06,780 --> 00:29:07,580
Mrs. Chu Junior,

791
00:29:07,580 --> 00:29:08,700
didn't you say

792
00:29:09,420 --> 00:29:10,940
good things don't happen in a hurry?

793
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:12,060
If it's meant to be finalized,

794
00:29:12,060 --> 00:29:13,620
a couple of days
won't make a difference.

795
00:29:13,740 --> 00:29:14,700
And if it's not going to happen,

796
00:29:14,700 --> 00:29:16,060
then there's even less reason to rush.

797
00:29:16,380 --> 00:29:17,660
Goodbye.

798
00:29:17,660 --> 00:29:18,340
No, wait.

799
00:29:18,540 --> 00:29:19,260
Mr. Chen.

800
00:29:19,900 --> 00:29:20,460
Dashun.

801
00:29:22,060 --> 00:29:22,660
Wait.

802
00:29:23,740 --> 00:29:24,660
Mr. Chen.

803
00:29:25,540 --> 00:29:27,700
Shaohua, see them off!

804
00:29:28,020 --> 00:29:29,820
They're leaving!

805
00:29:30,260 --> 00:29:31,140
Shaohua!

806
00:29:31,860 --> 00:29:32,980
Wait, Mr. Chen.

807
00:29:34,220 --> 00:29:34,980
Shaohua!

808
00:29:40,140 --> 00:29:41,420
Chu Shaohua, get out here!

809
00:29:42,860 --> 00:29:43,540
Chu Shaohua!

810
00:29:43,980 --> 00:29:44,620
Yan.

811
00:29:44,700 --> 00:29:46,540
What did they say?

812
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:48,300
They're calling off the wedding!

813
00:29:48,420 --> 00:29:49,660
They don't want your daughter anymore!

814
00:29:50,220 --> 00:29:51,420
And Shaozhong is a lost cause!

815
00:29:52,580 --> 00:29:53,340
Chu Shaohua!

816
00:29:53,660 --> 00:29:56,820
How are we supposed to save him now?

817
00:29:56,820 --> 00:29:57,460
Get out here!

818
00:29:58,340 --> 00:30:00,980
Chu Shaohua, they came to our door,

819
00:30:01,260 --> 00:30:02,580
and you locked yourself in.

820
00:30:02,740 --> 00:30:03,580
What do you mean by that?

821
00:30:04,180 --> 00:30:05,540
Not even coming out to greet them?

822
00:30:05,580 --> 00:30:06,980
Are you trying

823
00:30:06,980 --> 00:30:07,980
to ruin this marriage arrangement?

824
00:30:08,620 --> 00:30:10,420
I don't want to marry Chen Dashun.

825
00:30:11,460 --> 00:30:13,420
If you don't, Shaozhong will die.

826
00:30:16,380 --> 00:30:17,860
They don't want to marry me either.

827
00:30:18,700 --> 00:30:19,220
Wait.

828
00:30:22,180 --> 00:30:22,740
I...

829
00:30:23,300 --> 00:30:23,900
Fine.

830
00:30:23,900 --> 00:30:25,300
If you won't think about Shaozhong,

831
00:30:25,540 --> 00:30:27,220
then at least think
about your own future.

832
00:30:27,220 --> 00:30:28,580
Chu Shaohua, I'm telling you.

833
00:30:28,740 --> 00:30:29,940
With your looks,

834
00:30:29,940 --> 00:30:31,180
landing someone from the Chen family

835
00:30:31,180 --> 00:30:32,740
is already more than lucky.

836
00:30:32,940 --> 00:30:34,980
What kind of airs are you putting on?

837
00:30:35,100 --> 00:30:37,220
Don't tell me
you're never getting married

838
00:30:37,260 --> 00:30:39,900
and just sitting here
eating whatever's left, huh?

839
00:30:40,140 --> 00:30:40,900
I can't believe it.

840
00:30:41,300 --> 00:30:43,140
Shaozhong was so good to you
for nothing.

841
00:30:43,980 --> 00:30:45,060
You ungrateful wretch.

842
00:30:46,060 --> 00:30:47,660
Shaozhong always

843
00:30:47,660 --> 00:30:48,780
had you in mind.

844
00:30:48,900 --> 00:30:51,140
He's in serious trouble right now.

845
00:30:51,260 --> 00:30:53,700
How can you just turn away like this?

846
00:30:53,820 --> 00:30:54,300
Take it

847
00:30:55,220 --> 00:30:56,980
and buy whatever you want.

848
00:30:56,980 --> 00:30:57,780
I don't need that, Shaozhong.

849
00:30:58,620 --> 00:30:59,300
Just take it.

850
00:31:00,140 --> 00:31:01,420
Don't tell Yan.

851
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:06,740
Are you going to watch him die?

852
00:31:08,540 --> 00:31:10,860
If anything happens to Shaozhong,

853
00:31:10,860 --> 00:31:12,420
what about me and this child

854
00:31:12,420 --> 00:31:14,420
in my belly?

855
00:31:18,420 --> 00:31:19,260
Mother!

856
00:31:19,260 --> 00:31:20,700
Tell her to be reasonable!

857
00:31:20,700 --> 00:31:22,100
How can she act like this?

858
00:31:22,100 --> 00:31:23,700
She's too selfish!

859
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:26,300
Shaohua.

860
00:31:26,980 --> 00:31:29,060
I beg you.

861
00:31:29,260 --> 00:31:31,740
You must help Shaozhong.

862
00:31:32,180 --> 00:31:34,460
He's always been there for you.

863
00:31:35,140 --> 00:31:36,900
You can't just stand by and do nothing.

864
00:31:36,900 --> 00:31:39,420
You must help him!

865
00:31:39,620 --> 00:31:40,820
I beg you!

866
00:31:50,900 --> 00:31:51,540
She...

867
00:31:53,900 --> 00:31:54,460
Father!

868
00:31:55,340 --> 00:31:57,220
The woman
who spotted the fake Huangqi

869
00:31:57,660 --> 00:31:58,460
and helped us avoid

870
00:31:58,460 --> 00:32:00,020
a huge loss

871
00:32:01,060 --> 00:32:02,140
was Shaohua.

872
00:32:03,500 --> 00:32:04,420
Are you sure?

873
00:32:04,500 --> 00:32:06,260
I remember her face.

874
00:32:09,780 --> 00:32:12,380
Later,

875
00:32:13,420 --> 00:32:15,260
send some more thank-you gifts.

876
00:32:18,980 --> 00:32:19,580
Father.

877
00:32:20,380 --> 00:32:22,500
What about our marriage?

878
00:32:23,860 --> 00:32:24,780
Just keep stalling.

879
00:32:26,140 --> 00:32:27,900
If we drag it out for a year,

880
00:32:28,580 --> 00:32:30,820
they'll be the ones backing out.

881
00:32:31,580 --> 00:32:33,500
Shaohua's not bad.

882
00:32:33,620 --> 00:32:35,340
I didn't say she was.

883
00:32:35,340 --> 00:32:37,780
But no matter how good she is,

884
00:32:38,500 --> 00:32:39,780
her family's a problem.

885
00:32:39,780 --> 00:32:41,300
You saw it yourself.

886
00:32:42,060 --> 00:32:43,700
Marrying her

887
00:32:43,900 --> 00:32:46,540
will only bring endless problems.

888
00:32:46,540 --> 00:32:48,420
Walk away now

889
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:49,900
before it's too late.

890
00:33:05,420 --> 00:33:06,700
How did you get ahead of us?

891
00:33:06,700 --> 00:33:09,260
I took a shortcut through the village.

892
00:33:09,260 --> 00:33:09,980
Miss Chu.

893
00:33:11,220 --> 00:33:12,060
Is there anything else?

894
00:33:12,220 --> 00:33:16,340
Mr. Chen, I came to return this to you.

895
00:33:18,260 --> 00:33:20,580
Let's call off

896
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:22,180
the engagement.

897
00:33:22,580 --> 00:33:24,780
It was all set.

898
00:33:25,020 --> 00:33:26,980
How can it just be called off like that?

899
00:33:27,980 --> 00:33:28,820
Miss Chu.

900
00:33:30,140 --> 00:33:31,340
Have you thought it through?

901
00:33:32,100 --> 00:33:34,540
Marriage is about compatibility,
family, background, and status.

902
00:33:34,820 --> 00:33:36,740
Look at where you stand

903
00:33:36,740 --> 00:33:37,740
and where we do.

904
00:33:37,740 --> 00:33:38,980
It's plain to see.

905
00:33:39,420 --> 00:33:40,700
This isn't snobbery.

906
00:33:40,780 --> 00:33:43,180
It's just reality.

907
00:33:43,740 --> 00:33:44,420
Besides,

908
00:33:44,820 --> 00:33:47,340
even if you unwillingly let me
marry into your family,

909
00:33:48,060 --> 00:33:49,780
you'd still hold it against me.

910
00:33:50,100 --> 00:33:52,300
So I'd rather end it now.

911
00:33:52,300 --> 00:33:55,420
What about your mother
and sister-in-law?

912
00:33:55,980 --> 00:33:57,980
I make my own choices.

913
00:33:58,380 --> 00:34:00,060
Even if my father were still alive,

914
00:34:00,780 --> 00:34:02,860
I would handle it this way
if I wanted to.

915
00:34:04,380 --> 00:34:04,900
Father.

916
00:34:05,380 --> 00:34:06,380
I told you so.

917
00:34:06,540 --> 00:34:08,740
She's got real backbone.

918
00:34:09,860 --> 00:34:10,460
Alright.

919
00:34:11,420 --> 00:34:12,740
Since you've thought it through,

920
00:34:14,620 --> 00:34:15,900
I will grant your wish.

921
00:34:20,340 --> 00:34:20,860
Father.

922
00:34:22,620 --> 00:34:23,700
From now on,

923
00:34:24,220 --> 00:34:26,900
you and Dashun

924
00:34:27,420 --> 00:34:28,420
will go your separate ways.

925
00:34:28,860 --> 00:34:29,420
Father.

926
00:34:29,420 --> 00:34:30,340
That's good.

927
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:32,220
Mr. Chen, Dashun,

928
00:34:32,660 --> 00:34:33,660
I won't see you off.

929
00:34:33,660 --> 00:34:35,300
You go ahead. I'll be off.

930
00:34:35,300 --> 00:34:35,900
Shaohua.

931
00:34:36,620 --> 00:34:37,220
Shaohua.

932
00:34:37,380 --> 00:34:38,020
Shaohua.

933
00:34:38,300 --> 00:34:38,900
Father.

934
00:34:38,940 --> 00:34:40,220
Why would you do that?

935
00:34:40,420 --> 00:34:40,980
Father.

936
00:34:42,540 --> 00:34:43,380
Oh, Mr. Chen.

937
00:34:46,380 --> 00:34:49,060
Though the engagement was called off,

938
00:34:49,220 --> 00:34:52,540
if my brother and sister-in-law

939
00:34:53,180 --> 00:34:54,260
find out,

940
00:34:54,260 --> 00:34:56,100
they'll probably make
unreasonable demands.

941
00:34:56,260 --> 00:34:57,820
You don't need to entertain them.

942
00:34:58,380 --> 00:35:01,180
Just say I ended the engagement.

943
00:35:02,340 --> 00:35:03,980
And that you didn't ask for compensation

944
00:35:03,980 --> 00:35:05,380
is already very generous of you.

945
00:35:05,820 --> 00:35:07,940
If they keep bothering you,

946
00:35:08,220 --> 00:35:10,620
please have someone let me know.

947
00:35:10,980 --> 00:35:12,180
I will find a way myself

948
00:35:12,180 --> 00:35:13,740
to make them drop this idea.

949
00:35:14,380 --> 00:35:15,060
Shaohua,

950
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:18,140
I can provide some money

951
00:35:18,500 --> 00:35:19,620
to help you a little.

952
00:35:20,940 --> 00:35:21,660
Please don't.

953
00:35:25,220 --> 00:35:26,180
My father blew through all our money

954
00:35:27,460 --> 00:35:30,540
because it came too easily.

955
00:35:31,900 --> 00:35:33,620
My brother got into trouble
because he always thought

956
00:35:33,620 --> 00:35:34,980
good fortune just fell from the sky.

957
00:35:35,540 --> 00:35:37,460
That's why I can't accept help

958
00:35:37,460 --> 00:35:38,420
that I didn't earn.

959
00:35:39,180 --> 00:35:40,420
Father, see?

960
00:35:50,300 --> 00:35:52,180
You've got real backbone.

961
00:35:53,060 --> 00:35:53,700
