969
00:36:17,780 --> 00:36:18,700
I know how to use an abacus.

970
00:36:19,900 --> 00:36:20,980
I'm good at arithmetic.

971
00:36:21,180 --> 00:36:22,300
I can write.

972
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:25,260
And I've got basic knowledge
of medicine.

973
00:36:34,860 --> 00:36:35,660
Miss Chu.

974
00:36:37,100 --> 00:36:38,740
About the marriage,

975
00:36:39,660 --> 00:36:40,700
we've decided

976
00:36:41,220 --> 00:36:42,300
to go through with it.

977
00:36:43,420 --> 00:36:45,660
