982
00:36:58,300 --> 00:36:59,340
No need.

983
00:37:01,940 --> 00:37:02,700
Go back.

984
00:37:03,900 --> 00:37:05,180
Don't make your mother worry.

985
00:37:05,740 --> 00:37:07,260
Dashun, let's go.

986
00:37:07,580 --> 00:37:08,380
Go back.

987
00:37:44,140 --> 00:37:45,100
I'm glad you made it back.

988
00:37:45,260 --> 00:37:46,220
Well, Mother,

989
00:37:46,700 --> 00:37:48,260
Shaozhong's finally back
after everything.

990
00:37:48,500 --> 00:37:49,900
We should celebrate, don't you think?

991
00:37:50,260 --> 00:37:52,140
Let's go to the market tomorrow
and get some meat.

992
00:37:52,580 --> 00:37:53,980
How much would that cost?

993
00:37:54,300 --> 00:37:56,580
Mother, he could really use
a proper meal.

994
00:37:56,580 --> 00:37:59,260
Mother, I need some meat
to get my strength back.

995
00:37:59,260 --> 00:38:00,420
I lost a lot of blood.

996
00:38:00,740 --> 00:38:01,340
Alright.

997
00:38:01,860 --> 00:38:02,540
Alright.

998
00:38:15,660 --> 00:38:16,420
Shaohua.

999
00:38:17,220 --> 00:38:18,100
It's really late.

1000
00:38:18,100 --> 00:38:19,060
Why are you still up?

1001
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:19,900
Come with me.

1002
00:38:27,740 --> 00:38:29,140
Where exactly are you going?

1003
00:38:30,500 --> 00:38:31,300
Peking.

1004
00:38:31,420 --> 00:38:32,180
Peking?

1005
00:38:32,620 --> 00:38:34,100
You're always talking

1006
00:38:34,460 --> 00:38:36,620
about how great Peking is.

1007
00:38:37,020 --> 00:38:38,420
Now I get to see it for myself.

1008
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:40,820
Peking is huge.

1009
00:38:41,260 --> 00:38:42,300
Are you going alone?

1010
00:38:45,660 --> 00:38:46,860
Who else?

1011
00:38:47,980 --> 00:38:48,740
Wu.

1012
00:38:49,380 --> 00:38:50,620
Who is Wu?

1013
00:38:51,140 --> 00:38:52,580
He's from Daxinzhuang.

1014
00:38:52,900 --> 00:38:54,660
He used to work at Shouyuan Apothecary.

1015
00:38:55,820 --> 00:38:57,300
So that day at the Medicine Market

1016
00:38:57,620 --> 00:38:58,860
when you suddenly disappeared,

1017
00:38:59,140 --> 00:39:00,620
you actually went to meet him.

1018
00:39:01,940 --> 00:39:03,220
How long have you two been together?

1019
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:06,580
A month.

1020
00:39:07,260 --> 00:39:08,180
Just a month?

1021
00:39:08,420 --> 00:39:10,020
And you're already leaving with him?

1022
00:39:10,620 --> 00:39:11,500
He's good to me.

1023
00:39:12,140 --> 00:39:13,940
No, Erniu, you can't go.

1024
00:39:14,380 --> 00:39:15,460
Why not?

1025
00:39:15,980 --> 00:39:17,300
What if he lets you down?

1026
00:39:17,860 --> 00:39:18,620
Shaohua.

1027
00:39:19,740 --> 00:39:21,020
You're

1028
00:39:22,340 --> 00:39:24,020
the one who's been the kindest to me.

1029
00:39:25,300 --> 00:39:26,380
And then there's Wu.

1030
00:39:27,500 --> 00:39:28,900
I know he won't let me down.

1031
00:39:31,300 --> 00:39:33,820
I still think it is too risky.

1032
00:39:35,180 --> 00:39:36,180
Even so,

1033
00:39:37,580 --> 00:39:38,420
I still want to go.

1034
00:39:42,540 --> 00:39:43,940
Shaohua, you told me

1035
00:39:45,220 --> 00:39:47,060
you were afraid
of being trapped here your whole life.

1036
00:39:48,740 --> 00:39:50,060
Actually, I'm scared too.

1037
00:39:51,740 --> 00:39:53,380
If I stay here any longer,

1038
00:39:54,300 --> 00:39:56,260
my father will beat me to death.

1039
00:39:56,780 --> 00:39:58,020
Or worse, he'll sell me off

1040
00:39:58,060 --> 00:39:59,340
to be some old man's concubine.

1041
00:40:01,540 --> 00:40:02,500
Going with Wu

1042
00:40:03,060 --> 00:40:05,500
is my only chance to get out.

1043
00:40:11,620 --> 00:40:12,420
I'm leaving.

1044
00:40:14,100 --> 00:40:14,900
Erniu.

1045
00:40:23,780 --> 00:40:26,300
- The groom is here!
- The groom is here!

1046
00:40:26,540 --> 00:40:32,820
- The groom is here!
- The groom is here!

1047
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:57,180
Miss.

1048
00:41:05,900 --> 00:41:06,940
How much is the fee?

1049
00:41:10,980 --> 00:41:12,780
Are you bandits or rebels?

1050
00:41:13,860 --> 00:41:14,860
We are not bandits.

1051
00:41:15,180 --> 00:41:15,820
Shaohua,

1052
00:41:16,060 --> 00:41:17,380
with your intelligence and courage,

1053
00:41:17,660 --> 00:41:18,980
you'll achieve great things

1054
00:41:19,540 --> 00:41:20,500
as long as you're willing
to take the first step.

1055
00:41:21,460 --> 00:41:22,140
When I come back,

1056
00:41:22,580 --> 00:41:23,860
I'll take you to see the world outside,

1057
00:41:24,580 --> 00:41:25,340
okay?

1058
00:41:25,940 --> 00:41:26,580
Okay.

1059
00:41:26,980 --> 00:41:27,620
It's a promise.

1060
00:41:27,620 --> 00:41:28,500
You have my word.

1061
00:41:34,020 --> 00:41:34,620
Wait for me!

