I heard

1068
00:41:55,460 --> 00:41:56,900
Mr. Xia Chu was a revolutionary.

1069
00:41:56,940 --> 00:41:57,780
Really?

1070
00:41:57,780 --> 00:42:00,300
He tried to assassinate
a first-rank duke with a bomb

1071
00:42:00,980 --> 00:42:02,940
