♪Each page turns, life's folded lines♪

1078
00:42:32,340 --> 00:42:39,020
♪I may sigh through the rest of my life♪

1079
00:42:39,340 --> 00:42:45,020
♪Yet my heart won't close its door♪

1080
00:42:45,260 --> 00:42:51,060
♪That fleeting light I failed to chase♪

1081
