♪Seeking the shore within my soul♪

1086
00:43:22,060 --> 00:43:24,460
♪Winds howl wild♪

1087
00:43:24,620 --> 00:43:28,340
♪My soul, near torn♪

1088
00:43:29,060 --> 00:43:35,500
♪A blanket hidden deep within his heart♪

1089
